<% tickets = @order.tickets.reject(&:canceled_at?) %>
<% unassigned = tickets.reject(&:assigned?) %>
Your Deccan Queen on Rails order

Hello <%= @order.buyer_name %>,

Here is the permanent link to order <%= @order.code %>. Bookmark it — it is where
you download your tickets and tax invoice, and where you name your attendees:

<%= order_url(@order.code) %>
<% if unassigned.any? %>
<%= pluralize(unassigned.size, "ticket") %> still <%= unassigned.one? ? "has" : "have" %> nobody named on <%= unassigned.one? ? "it" : "them" %>. Assign them from the
link above, or send an attendee their own private link below so they fill in
their own name, dietary needs, T-shirt size and childcare.
<% else %>
All <%= pluralize(tickets.size, "ticket") %> already have an attendee. If anything needs correcting,
use the links below.
<% end %>
<% tickets.each do |ticket| %>
- <%= ticket.ticket_type.name %><%= " — #{ticket.attendee_name}" if ticket.assigned? %>
  <%= ticket_claim_url(ticket.claim_token) %>
<% end %>

See you in Pune.
